bonfyre-narrate v3.2 — verified tone-aware text-to-speech synthesis

Usage:
  bonfyre-narrate <text-file> <output-dir> [options]
  bonfyre-narrate verify <output.wav> <source-features.json>

Options:
  --voice-model PATH        Piper ONNX model path
  --tone-profile PATH       Tone profile JSON (bonfyre-tone profile)
  --source-features PATH    88-feature tone.json (bonfyre-tone extract)
  --verify                  Run closed-loop fidelity verification
  --refine [TARGET]         Iterative refinement (default: 0.85)
  --audio-format FMT        Output format (default: wav)
  --title TITLE             Artifact title
  --ssml                    Generate SSML
  --dry-run                 Print plan without generating audio
  --no-pitch-shift          Skip PSOLA pitch correction
  --no-envelope             Skip energy envelope transfer

Verification pipeline:
  bonfyre-tone extract audio.wav tone_out/
  bonfyre-tone profile audio.wav tone_out/
  bonfyre-narrate summary.md narrate_out/ \
    --tone-profile tone_out/profile.json \
    --source-features tone_out/tone.json \
    --verify --refine

6-layer fidelity scoring. Closed-loop quality verification.
